data.description: Welcome home to this truly stunning and immaculate home with the latest in luxury and efficiency! This single-story home features 3-bedrooms, plus an office and 2-full bathrooms with gorgeous landscaping and a fully-owned SOLAR system. Amenities include: Gourmet-inspired kitchen with slab granite counter tops/backsplash, maple cabinets with pull outs, a mammoth-sized island and stainless steel appliances and double sink; The vibrant dining area is open to the great room flanked with a gas/wood burning fireplace, surround sound speakers and built-in entertainers niche; The luxurious master suite has a large, relaxing bathroom with a large soaking tub, separate shower and an oversized closet; Upgraded oversized tile flooring; Upgraded carpet/padding; Custom paint; Ceiling fans and lights; Custom window treatments; Indoor laundry room with extra cabinets/counter space; 3-Car Tandem Garage with Epoxy flooring and sink; The tranquil backyard retreat includes an Alumawood patio cover with lights, ceiling fan and drapery, water feature, grape vines and raised garden boxes, lush landscaping and flowers and block-wall fencing. All this...and walking distance to Dairyland Park, convenient access to freeways, shopping and schools. NO HOA â?" Make this home YOUR OWN!
